CSSMathNegate.summary: The CSSMathNegate interface of the CSS Typed Object Model API negates the value passed into it. It inherits properties and methods from its parent .

CSSMathNegateCSSMathNegate.summary:
The CSSMathNegate() constructor creates a
new object which negates the value passed into it.

CSSMathNegateValue.summary:
The CSSMathNegate.value read-only property of the
interface returns a object.
